{"id":14881048,"mediaExerciseId":"a8a0a30f-3f41-4ff6-9c4e-bb4649e034a0","exerciseName":"14","chapterName":"7","chapterTitle":"Interest Rates and Bond Valuation","groupId":612312,"groupTitle":"Critical Thinking Questions","isPremium":true,"sectionName":null,"sectionTitle":null,"pageNumber":233,"solutions":[{"id":5985699,"modifiedOn":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000000","steps":[{"columns":[{"text":"This task asks to explain **why bond rating agencies should not provide a service voluntarily.**","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":68,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/05/d86d85e1f5cb05ff61368656b59fd043/921a8f19687d75452f2d1f14a3c5dfd5/lateximg_large.png","width":996},"regular":{"height":34,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/05/d86d85e1f5cb05ff61368656b59fd043/921a8f19687d75452f2d1f14a3c5dfd5/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":1},{"columns":[{"text":"**Investors put a high value on the results of bond rating agencies before investing in a specified company.** That shows us how important is the evaluation of the rating agencies. *The service's price reflects how professionally and efficiently the whole evaluation process is done*. Therefore, **investors would consider unprofessionalism and not include all the necessary factors in the calculation for agencies that are providing their services for free. The demand for such bond rating agencies will decrease**.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":256,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/05/d86d85e1f5cb05ff61368656b59fd043/f40e51494d77c5911f4328f7a1113ab2/lateximg_large.png","width":1035},"regular":{"height":128,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/05/d86d85e1f5cb05ff61368656b59fd043/f40e51494d77c5911f4328f7a1113ab2/lateximg.png","width":518}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":2}],"rating":5,"solutionUuid":"469cd